  "detailed_description": "Explore the Egyptian underworld in this precision platformer by leveraging the power of ancient gods!<br><br>Conquer <strong>over 200 rooms</strong> spread across <strong>tombs and otherworldly biomes</strong>, with each zone presenting unique challenges.<br>                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/21c2fce9875abe3ef7b88b63702f89f0.poster.avif?t=1744022281\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/21c2fce9875abe3ef7b88b63702f89f0.webm?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/21c2fce9875abe3ef7b88b63702f89f0.mp4?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Traverse the underworld in style with <strong>ancient powers</strong> which grant hover, wall jump, and dash abilities.<br>                             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/47bceb9695db8129bf47220d9e0f6273.poster.avif?t=1744022281\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/47bceb9695db8129bf47220d9e0f6273.webm?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/47bceb9695db8129bf47220d9e0f6273.mp4?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Worried about death? Mystical ankh statues will <strong>quickly resurrect</strong> you so you can retry challenges right away.<br>                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/b926e88ed0d275142371eda7af82796c.poster.avif?t=1744022281\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/b926e88ed0d275142371eda7af82796c.webm?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/b926e88ed0d275142371eda7af82796c.mp4?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Battle <strong>terrifying gods</strong> and befriend <strong>charming creatures</strong> who call the underworld their home.<br>                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/283f6d43b14ada29e305251fd7b80c67.poster.avif?t=1744022281\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/283f6d43b14ada29e305251fd7b80c67.webm?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874550/extras/283f6d43b14ada29e305251fd7b80c67.mp4?t=1744022281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
